08:13.493 --> 08:14.619
Maynard?

08:14.911 --> 08:16.579
Connie? What's going on?

08:17.330 --> 08:18.540
What are you doing here?

08:20.542 --> 08:21.894
In my home?

08:21.918 --> 08:23.211
No, I mean now.

08:24.045 --> 08:25.672
I wanted to surprise you.

08:27.674 --> 08:30.111
You know, I'm just
gonna take off.

08:30.135 --> 08:31.261
Jack?

08:31.553 --> 08:34.155
- Is that...? What's going on?
- I can explain this.

08:34.179 --> 08:37.350
You can explain why you're
dressed up like a rabbit

08:37.517 --> 08:39.184
and having sex with a squirrel?

08:39.436 --> 08:41.455
- I'm a wolf.
- We don't have sex.

08:41.479 --> 08:43.879
That's right. According to the
club, you can't even have sex.

08:45.233 --> 08:48.754
- Club? What club is this?
- Well, it's the kind of club where...

08:48.778 --> 08:51.215
You-dress-up-like-a-squirrel-
and-have-sex-my-wife club?

08:51.239 --> 08:52.532
I'm a wolf.

08:52.782 --> 08:54.427
How many people are in the club?

08:54.451 --> 08:58.413
Well, in the tri-county area we got...
what is it, 32?

08:59.372 --> 09:01.892
Look, I've been meaning to
talk to you for a while.

09:01.916 --> 09:03.918
A while? How long has
this been going on?

09:04.085 --> 09:08.024
That's not important, Maynard. What
is important is that I'm bored.

09:08.048 --> 09:11.235
Get a hobby! Learn
to knit, do macramé.

09:11.259 --> 09:13.529
- Are you kidding me?
- We don't do anything!

09:13.553 --> 09:16.907
We don't go anywhere! I need
some excitement in my life!

09:16.931 --> 09:20.119
So instead of talking to me about
it, somewhere in your brain,

09:20.143 --> 09:21.895
the thing that makes
sense, is to go out

09:22.228 --> 09:24.022
and have sex with a squirrel?

09:24.189 --> 09:25.273
I'm a wolf!

09:27.692 --> 09:30.921
Get it? It doesn't make
any sense as a squirrel!

09:30.945 --> 09:32.048
It's gotta be a wolf!

09:32.072 --> 09:33.674
Jack, we have been
friends forever.

09:33.698 --> 09:34.699
I know.

09:37.994 --> 09:39.972
That's why I'm gonna need
to ask a favor of you.

09:39.996 --> 09:41.348
Sure thing, whatever
you need, buddy.

09:41.372 --> 09:43.208
You know, I'm kind of a
big deal in this town

09:43.333 --> 09:46.419
and don't think it'd be good
if people knew I was a furry.

09:47.295 --> 09:48.379
What's a furry?

09:49.255 --> 09:51.382
Furry. It's this
club we belong to.

09:52.217 --> 09:54.779
Well, don't 32 other
people already know?

09:54.803 --> 09:57.722
Seriously, Maynard, okay? I'm
gonna need your word on this.

10:02.185 --> 10:05.185
I think we need to take some time apart
and think about what we really want.

10:11.402 --> 10:14.739
Maynard! Maynard! You're gonna
have to keep a tight lip on this.

10:16.074 --> 10:17.909
I'm kind of a big
deal around here.

10:20.912 --> 10:22.747
- Well, I am.
- I know.

