10:57.866 --> 10:59.951
I was just about to
call it a night.

11:01.161 --> 11:02.996
That's why you're the best.

11:03.580 --> 11:04.747
Are you drunk?

11:06.166 --> 11:11.004
First time since my wedding night,
and we all know how that turned out.

11:11.379 --> 11:13.464
I don't understand.
What happened?

11:15.341 --> 11:16.342
