11:17.677 --> 11:19.888
I went out to breathe
some life...

11:20.680 --> 11:23.850
and then life decided to
take a poop on my face.

11:23.975 --> 11:27.937
So, I ended up breathing
poop instead.

11:28.646 --> 11:30.857
Rabbit and squirrel
poop, to be precise.

11:31.149 --> 11:33.276
What? Maynard, you're
not making any sense.

11:34.319 --> 11:37.006
You're right! Because
he wasn't a squirrel.

11:37.030 --> 11:39.699
He was a wolf! He's a wolf.

11:44.245 --> 11:48.166
Doesn't work if he's a squirrel.
It only works if he's a wolf.

11:48.958 --> 11:51.187
Sorry for the confusion.
It was a wolf.

11:51.211 --> 11:52.730
Let's make you some coffee.

11:52.754 --> 11:56.382
- No, I want my moonshine.
- Okay.

11:56.841 --> 11:58.176
Bart gave me this.

12:06.476 --> 12:08.954
This stuff is making me crazy.

12:08.978 --> 12:12.023
- No argument here.
- It's okay, Parker.

12:12.148 --> 12:17.779
'Cause you gotta get crazy sometime,
because of the speeding little rock.

12:24.827 --> 12:26.955
- You want some?
- No, I think I'm good.

12:27.538 --> 12:29.290
Let's get you home.

12:32.293 --> 12:33.711
I don't have a home.

12:34.963 --> 12:38.859
Of course you do and Connie's
gonna be worried sick.

12:38.883 --> 12:40.134
There's no Connie.

12:42.345 --> 12:46.516
She's been replaced by the
Easter Bunny's evil twin.

12:50.186 --> 12:51.271
She left me.

12:52.021 --> 12:53.021
What?

12:55.441 --> 12:56.442
Yeah.

12:58.820 --> 13:00.363
Oh, Maynard.

13:02.865 --> 13:04.367
I'm so sorry.

13:07.245 --> 13:08.746
Is there anything that...?

13:09.580 --> 13:11.332
Is there anything that I can...?

13:14.419 --> 13:15.586
No.

13:16.671 --> 13:18.047
I just wanna sit here.

13:19.257 --> 13:21.259
Let me take you
back to my place.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.511
It's fine.

13:25.179 --> 13:26.306
It's fine.

13:27.015 --> 13:29.142
I just wanna be here alone...

13:30.184 --> 13:32.937
think about wolves,
and rocks, and stuff.

13:33.396 --> 13:35.398
You sure you don't want
me to stay with you?

13:36.024 --> 13:37.525
Let me ask you a question.

13:37.734 --> 13:39.235
This is very important.

13:39.861 --> 13:40.861
Okay.

13:42.530 --> 13:44.532
Do you belong to a
furry sex club?

13:45.074 --> 13:46.743
I think you'll be
fine by yourself.

13:48.411 --> 13:50.431
- It's important to me.
- Yeah.

13:50.455 --> 13:53.976
I don't want you to wind up
like a furry animal sex freak.

13:54.000 --> 13:56.520
I'm gonna come back first
thing in the morning, okay?

13:56.544 --> 13:59.088
And you do me a favor
and get some rest.

14:00.590 --> 14:01.716
Okay?

14:20.526 --> 14:22.236
You were right, my friend.

14:24.280 --> 14:26.449
Here's to going crazy.

14:51.307 --> 14:52.392
All right...

14:53.476 --> 14:56.437
I'll play freaky forest
animals with ya.

16:01.127 --> 16:05.840
You know what a gorilla
would do to a bunny,

16:06.507 --> 16:08.718
or a squirrel, or whatever?

16:10.470 --> 16:11.929
Eat them alive!

16:39.332 --> 16:40.791
Maynard?

16:40.917 --> 16:42.752
Oh! Maynard, you should get up!

16:43.127 --> 16:45.838
Okay? I'll just...
I'll shut the door.

16:46.047 --> 16:47.089
Bunny.

16:47.798 --> 16:48.798
Squirrels.

16:49.050 --> 16:50.134
Gorilla.

16:55.515 --> 16:57.016
What are all these
people doing here?

16:57.517 --> 16:59.161
And now, for a story on a...

16:59.185 --> 17:00.185
You gotta see this.

17:00.561 --> 17:03.814
We go out live to Stacy
Gutierrez for a special report.

17:04.190 --> 17:05.858
- Stacy.
- Thanks, John.

17:06.317 --> 17:09.069
Hi, this is Stacy Gutierrez,

17:09.487 --> 17:14.926
live in front of the once thriving,
but now abandoned, Pottersville Mill.

17:14.951 --> 17:17.304
I'm here with the
local townsfolk

17:17.328 --> 17:22.415
who claim to have witnessed what they're
calling, well, a Bigfoot sighting.

17:23.166 --> 17:24.853
So, tell me, what did you see?

17:24.877 --> 17:27.296
Well, we were all out in
the woods smoking a...

17:27.505 --> 17:28.631
You know, hanging out.

17:28.839 --> 17:31.175
When all of a sudden this
big, huge, hairy thing

17:31.592 --> 17:33.028
comes running by, screaming.

17:33.052 --> 17:35.304
We were like, "Hey,
how stoned are you?"

17:37.765 --> 17:42.645
And then we realized we all saw
it, and we were like... "cool."

17:42.979 --> 17:46.333
I was upstairs dozing off
when I heard her scream.

17:46.357 --> 17:49.503
I heard this ruckus in the
backyard and looked out the window

17:49.527 --> 17:52.488
and I saw this...
thing, chasing a bunny.

17:52.863 --> 17:54.365
I come running down the stairs,

17:54.657 --> 17:57.827
turned on the back porch
lights and there it was.

17:58.703 --> 18:00.496
We saw it. Squatch.

18:01.080 --> 18:03.433
You've lived here your
entire life, correct?

18:03.457 --> 18:05.209
Yes, ma'am, I have.

18:05.418 --> 18:07.232
Have you ever seen
anything like this before?

18:07.336 --> 18:10.965
No, ma'am. Like the kid said,
it was a big, hairy thing.

18:11.424 --> 18:14.010
Sort of half man, half gorilla.

18:14.844 --> 18:17.555
You know, like them cavemen you
see in the picture books...

18:18.639 --> 18:19.974
that ain't quite evolved yet.

18:20.474 --> 18:23.370
And all that chasing the bunny
must have made him pretty thirsty,

18:23.394 --> 18:27.440
'cause he was out there in our
little boy peeing fountain drinking.

18:27.773 --> 18:31.086
I mean, literally, the little boy
was peeing right in his mouth.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.153
Then what happened?

18:32.778 --> 18:35.406
Then he just disappeared
into the darkness.

18:35.948 --> 18:37.801
- There you have it, John.
- Can you believe that?

18:37.825 --> 18:40.971
- A pretty incredible story.
- Yeah, that's something.

18:40.995 --> 18:42.747
Bigfoot, right here,
in our own backyard.

18:42.997 --> 18:45.809
I might have to come up there to try
and catch a glimpse of him myself.

18:45.833 --> 18:46.876
That sucks.

18:47.126 --> 18:48.711
You should!

18:49.211 --> 18:50.338
I'll be right back.

18:50.880 --> 18:52.048
Is everything...?

19:35.049 --> 19:37.009
Sir, I'm sorry. Can
you pick up, please?

19:38.219 --> 19:39.196
Is he here?

19:39.220 --> 19:41.555
We have a bit of an emergency
going on right now, Maynard.

19:41.681 --> 19:43.408
Trust me, he's gonna
want to hear about this.

19:43.432 --> 19:44.684
All right. Go ahead.

19:45.184 --> 19:46.769
Ma'am, can you
repeat that, please?

19:47.061 --> 19:48.604
Sure. Absolutely.

19:52.650 --> 19:57.029
Yeah, well, we could either do it here in
my office, or go out to Phoebe's Knob.

19:57.530 --> 19:58.614
Four o'clock. Thank you.

19:59.407 --> 20:01.426
I was gonna talk to
you, man, I promise,

20:01.450 --> 20:04.078
but things are nuts
around here this morning.

20:04.412 --> 20:05.412
Yeah.

20:05.871 --> 20:08.416
Maynard, I'm not having
an affair with Connie.

20:09.542 --> 20:10.936
It's just about the club.

20:10.960 --> 20:13.880
I mean, hell, that could've been anybody
from the club up in your bedroom.

20:15.589 --> 20:17.192
Thanks. I feel a lot better now.

20:17.216 --> 20:19.051
There's nothing romantic.
I'd never do that.

20:19.927 --> 20:21.345
It's just about the costumes.

20:23.264 --> 20:24.432
Speaking of costumes...

20:25.558 --> 20:26.851
Sheriff, sorry to interrupt,

20:26.976 --> 20:30.312
but there's a producer from some
television show on the phone for you.

20:31.230 --> 20:33.816
Thanks, Tammy. Look, I've
gotta take this. But...

20:34.233 --> 20:35.460
We're okay, right?

20:35.484 --> 20:38.654
Hey, I'm never gonna rub the bunny again.
I promise.

20:39.447 --> 20:41.883
- I gotta show you something.
- I gotta take this.

20:41.907 --> 20:43.909
Everybody's apeshit over
this Bigfoot business.

20:44.118 --> 20:46.245
Later, okay? We'll
talk later, all right?

20:47.663 --> 20:50.750
Hello. Yeah, this
is Sheriff Clark.

20:51.417 --> 20:52.769
- Okay.
- Yeah.

20:52.793 --> 20:53.836
Hi, how are you?

20:56.297 --> 20:57.715
Good to hear your voice as well.

20:59.175 --> 21:03.012
Well, let's see. Maybe we
can make something work...

21:12.938 --> 21:14.541
Just the man we
were looking for.

21:14.565 --> 21:16.334
We were wondering if you
could do us a favor.

21:16.358 --> 21:19.755
Now, we've been researching this whole
Bigfoot thing, and people really love him.

21:19.779 --> 21:20.654
It's true.

21:20.780 --> 21:24.241
He's been around for centuries,
and people on every continent

21:24.492 --> 21:27.995
and that speak every language, they
just can't get enough of this guy.

21:28.162 --> 21:30.790
Yeah, so we've decided to get
into the Bigfoot business.

21:30.915 --> 21:34.227
We're gonna start this
whole cottage industry...

21:34.251 --> 21:37.773
Bigfoot t-shirts, hats, bumper
stickers, baby onesies, you name it.

21:37.797 --> 21:41.175
Everything. We were just wondering if
we could sell some stuff in your store?

21:43.177 --> 21:44.177
So, what do you think?

21:49.850 --> 21:51.602
Sure, fellas. Whatever you need.

21:53.103 --> 21:54.372
Awesome.

21:54.396 --> 21:55.481
Thanks.

21:58.734 --> 22:00.653
- Hey.
- Hey.

22:01.737 --> 22:04.174
I was wanting to talk to you about
last night. I've been thinking...

22:04.198 --> 22:06.551
I know we need to talk, Maynard,
I just can't right now.

22:06.575 --> 22:07.952
I've got something to do.

22:08.744 --> 22:11.372
- What's more important than...
- Bigfoot.

22:12.331 --> 22:14.250
Seriously? You
believe in all that?

22:14.750 --> 22:16.043
Are you kidding me?

22:16.627 --> 22:17.729
